"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-01-31-france-reduces-crowd-numbers-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP)- The French government announced Wednesday that it had slashed the crowd size for the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics this July amid security and other organisational worries.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.5268611216064725, \"rank\": 0.8215724219344821, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6704841737261288, \"rank\": 0.22574026038842657, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd size\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 97}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 144}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"other organisational worries\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The traditional opening parade for the Games is set to take place in boats on the river Seine on July 26, the first time a summer Olympics has opened outside the main athletics stadium.\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The traditional opening parade\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 278}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"a summer Olympics\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"the main athletics stadium\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After months of speculation about the number of people permitted to watch the flotilla, Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin told the France 2 channel on Tuesday \\\"around 300,000\\\" ticketed fans would attend.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"score\": 0.8959405678328872, \"rank\": 0.11448251985202589, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\"}, {\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999980640723701, \"rank\": 1.149897915618886e-06, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}, {\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France 2\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"speculation\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"the flotilla\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"around 300,000\\\" ticketed fans\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is half the 600,000 that Darmanin had suggested in 2022 and is even smaller than the most recent estimates of 400-500,000, underlining the complexity of securing an event over six kilometres (four miles) of river.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the most recent estimates\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"the complexity\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"six kilometres\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"four miles\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"river\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that we have the best security forces in the world and that we will succeed in showing not only that we can win medals (at the Olympics) but that we can play host to the world without any problems,\\\" Darmanin told the channel.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best security forces\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"any problems\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"the channel\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea of a spectacular open-air parade with hundreds of boats gave cold sweats to many in the French security establishment because of the difficulty of controling the crowds and the risk of terror attacks.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6704841737261288, \"rank\": 0.22574026038842657, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular open-air parade\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"cold sweats\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficulty\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"terror attacks\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers and the Paris mayor's office had initially imagined up to two million people in attendance, a source close to the negotiations told AFP.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.376096812888938e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999472320283, \"rank\": 5.249106763926538e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"two million people\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"attendance\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"the negotiations\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities have also had difficulties in persuading historic Parisian booksellers who line the river from temporarily removing their kiosks in order to make space for spectators.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Authorities\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulties\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"historic Parisian booksellers\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"their kiosks\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The artistic director in charge of the ceremony, theatre director Thomas Jolly, told AFP last week that contingency plans were in place in the event of a direct terror threat or severe weather.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9644589908671565, \"rank\": 0.02232539986716183, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 1677, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999472320283, \"rank\": 5.249106763926538e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The artistic director\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"contingency plans\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"a direct terror threat\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"severe weather\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have lots of different plans, but the location for the ceremony will remain the Seine,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999940223461, \"rank\": 5.977173214101881e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"different plans\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"the location\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Darmanin said that 100,000 tickets had been sold for the best vantage points on the lower banks of the river, while another 200,000 would be given free access to the upper banks.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"100,000 tickets\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"the best vantage points\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower banks\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"free access\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the upper banks\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The figure of 300,000 people did not include others \\\"who live and who will be able to rent to have parties along the Seine\\\", Darmanin added, referring to the hundreds of buildings that overlook the famed waterway.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999940223461, \"rank\": 5.977173214101881e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The figure\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"300,000 people\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"parties\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"the hundreds\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"the famed waterway\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The open-air boat parade is in keeping with promises to make the Paris Olympics \\\"iconic\\\", with the local organising committee keen to break from past traditions in the way it stages the world's biggest sporting event.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The open-air boat parade\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"promises\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"the local organising committee\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"past traditions\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest sporting event\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics ceremony is generally considered to be the most spectacular in history while the 2012 London ceremony, overseen by \\\"Trainspotting\\\" director Danny Boyle, won rave reviews for showcasing Britain's quirky side.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9964353989804707, \"rank\": 0.003577352796519317, \"text\": \"2012 London\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2676, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danny Boyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\"}, {\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998177948286039, \"rank\": 0.00013045745448202369, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics ceremony\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Trainspotting\\\" director\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"rave reviews\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The huge opening ceremony in Paris with hundreds of thousands of free tickets was also part of the organisers' vision of a \\\"people's Olympics\\\" that would be widely accessible to the public.\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2774, \"end\": 2779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.376096812888938e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The huge opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds of thousands\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"free tickets\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers' vision\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"people's Olympics\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That ambition has been undermined by high ticket prices for the sport, particularly for the athletics, leading to criticism from many Parisians.\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 3080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That ambition\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"high ticket prices\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletics\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3059}, {\"ngram\": \"many Parisians\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The head of the Paris capital region, Valerie Pecresse, welcomed Wednesday's downgrade of the opening ceremony to 300,000 people - still several times the number who usually witness the Olympics parade in an athletics stadium.\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3098, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.376096812888938e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3120, \"end\": 3127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\", \"score\": 0.9941821657605284, \"rank\": 0.00585187950419703, \"text\": \"Valerie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The head\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday's downgrade\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3192}, {\"ngram\": \"300,000 people\",